    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Golden Wings], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Golden Wings (Greater)], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Golden Wings (Major)], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Golden Wings (True)]</p>\n<p>You emit a bright light in a 20-foot radius and dim light for the next 20 feet. You take a –2 item penalty to Stealth checks to Hide and Sneak.</p>\n<p>When you activate <em>major golden wings</em>, you also gain a fly Speed of 20 feet.</p>\n<p>When you activate <em>true golden wings</em>, you also gain a fly Speed equal to your Speed or 25 feet, whichever is greater.</p>"
